Create `src/components/Icons.tsx` with all icon components as React FC:

**Required Icons:**
1. LogoIcon - Code bracket `</>` for header logo
2. LinkedInIcon - LinkedIn social icon
3. InstagramIcon - Instagram social icon  
4. MailIcon - Email icon
5. FooterLogoIcon - Letter "N" or brand icon for footer

**Implementation Pattern:**
```typescript
type IconProps = {
  className?: string;
};

export const LogoIcon: React.FC<IconProps> = ({ className }) => (
  <svg className={className} viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
    {/* SVG paths */}
  </svg>
);
```

**Guidelines:**
- All icons accept className prop for styling
- Use `fill="currentColor"` for color inheritance
- Default size: 24x24 viewBox
- Simple, clean SVG designs
- Export all icons individually

Update `src/app/globals.css` to add marquee keyframes:

**Add to bottom of file:**
```css
@keyframes marquee {
  0% {
    transform: translateX(0);
  }
  100% {
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
}
```

**Also add Tailwind layer for custom animation:**
```css
@layer utilities {
  .animate-marquee {
    animation: marquee 30s linear infinite;
  }
}
```

**Purpose:**
- Creates horizontal scrolling effect for tech logos
- Smooth infinite loop animation
- NO Framer Motion - pure CSS

**Note:** Content will be duplicated in component to create seamless loop

